subSubSection.paragraph:
Elytra (ElyL 
9.3 mm
) deeply striate; striae sparsely and equally punctate. Elytral intervals convex and strongly punctate; interval punctures dense, evenly distributed, and relatively equal in size; interval punctures slightly deeper than strial punctures. Each elytron with one rather abrupt vertical flattening near sutural angle.
